Trailer breakdown:
0:03 hero was a cop going for a mission
0:26 he was get caught by the gangster and he was been given poison by him, because he s not showing up himself from were he is coming from and what he was working for. This shows his loyalty.
0:34 the hero was transported to some facility were some wind mills are present.
(note- here all wind mills are rotating in) clockwise.
0:37 shows hero was screened up for some bigger mission by an organization. Here he was totally wiped out of his past. And it is a afterlife for him.
0:46 now the hero was trying to find what is happening in the facility.
0:50 a underground laboratory inside the ship were it all happens.
0:55 doctor with white coat says its about to stop world war three. The stone she shows with some bullet markings.
0:59 the man wears a oxygen mask shows it is about something carcinogenic
1:01 in next shot they say it is not about nuclear war represent it may be a biowar. That is y the man wearing a oxygen mask.
1:07 the hero is being pushed towards some machine it may be time traveling machine or teleportation machine.
1:11 after this the wind mill and ship was going in reverse motion so this represent it may something of parallel universe or the hero was teleported to the same place but everything happens in a reverse motion.
Now the title comes TENET means one of the principal on which a belief or theory is based. This represent hero is going to change the basic principle of existence to stop the third world war. That is reverse technology. project TENET.
1:18 says tenet may open right doors and some wrong doors too shows both good ppl in the ship and some bad ppl in next shot.
1:24 the military person is going in reverse motion.
1:25 hero alone walking in a reverse manner shows he is in the same place and time but due to the TENET experiment his body and mind works in a reverse manner.
1:27 oxygen mask again represent some viral carcinogen happenings.
1:29 lady says he should start looking the world in different way that is in a reverse manner.
1:30 the car reversely go and crash another car, but when hero was seeing the car was getting back to normal i.e) the crashed car was there but the accident was not happened yet.
1:53 man from the otherside of mirror asks what happened. For him it had happened but for hero from this side of the mirror it hadn't happened yet.
This shows both ppl know the result but for hero it is not happened yet. This also shows the hero was teleproted to the same place but working in a reverse manner.
Hero was 'N' and only he Can understand both 'TE' and mirror image of 'ET' ( sorry i cant put it in reverse manner) like user interface. that is why TENET as title.
So hero is going to the parallel universe were the world destroyed but the war didn't happened yet. Parallel universe here is nothing but the same place were the tenet person will have the reverse motion.
By this he can change the core principle he can change the whole belief.
Hero is traveling to the place were problem's result is there but the steps are not yet derived (note he is in the same place only the world changes)
Whether he stops the war or not will be the climax
Dont try to understand the movie feel it.

snippet.textDisplay: This is not time travel in the usual sense (going from point A to point B in an instant through a time machine) Here the arrow of  time is reversed for some characters. So when the world moves from point A to point B in time, these characters move from point B to point A. So for them, the world is moving in reverse.
